Title: I Belong here
DateModified: '2019-03-09'
DatePublished: '2019-03-09'
Url: https://www.worldnomads.com/create/scholarships/writing/2019/applications/i-belong-here
SetInCountry: India
Category: A leap into the unknown
AuthorName: Vatsala Gupta
AuthorCountry: India
Text: "The story is all about What exactly India is and meeting new people of diverse\
  \ culture ,different societies with variance lifestyles.\nMeeting them is exploring\
  \ the real India.\nThe First wonder of the World Taj Mahal is indeed a beautiful\
  \ and iconic.\nFrom Katra , Jammu to Kanyakumari this country is a real beauty.\n\
  Sanitation can be an issue but you should be all prepared for it.\nExploring the\
  \ historical places in Delhi to Meeting the Royals in Rajasthan, this country indeed\
  \ crowns the title of ATITHI DEVO BHAVA.\nSimply means GUEST IS GOD.\nThis beautiful\
  \ country consists of 29 states with different weathers and languages all around\
  \ .\nThe mainly spoken language is Hindi and English.\nDidn\u2019t get a chance\
  \ to explore the slum areas but met few of them to gather much of a story out of\
  \ them."
